<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 16:09:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>千载难逢的事件：一颗死去的恒星很快将为天文观测者带来一场精彩的表演</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/imminent-explosion-of-t-coronae-borealis-promises-skywatchers-a-stellar-show/articleshow/108825364.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108825364.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 13:38:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/imminent-explosion-of-t-coronae-borealis-promises-skywatchers-a-stellar-show/articleshow/108825364.cms</guid></item><item><title>为什么俄罗斯“很难相信”伊斯兰国袭击了莫斯科</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/why-russia-finds-it-hard-to-believe-that-isis-attacked-moscow/articleshow/108826769.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108826769.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 14:50:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/why-russia-finds-it-hard-to-believe-that-isis-attacked-moscow/articleshow/108826769.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦将对造成5名中国公民死亡的炸弹袭击者进行DNA检测</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-to-conduct-dna-testing-on-remains-of-suicide-bomber-who-killed-5-chinese-nationals/articleshow/108819016.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108819016.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦已授权对上拉地区自杀式炸弹袭击者的遗体进行DNA检测，该袭击造成5名中国公民和一名当地司机死亡。该地区对中巴经济走廊至关重要，大苏大坝等项目的工人在这里工作。巴基斯坦总理谢赫巴兹·谢里夫在与中国大使江再冬的讨论中保证迅速解决这一问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 11:08:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-to-conduct-dna-testing-on-remains-of-suicide-bomber-who-killed-5-chinese-nationals/articleshow/108819016.cms</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩火箭弹杀死以色列北部平民</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/lebanon-rocket-kills-civilian-in-northern-israel/articleshow/108816514.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108816514.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列医疗组织 Magen David Adom 表示，周三，一枚从黎巴嫩发射的火箭炸死了一名被困在以色列北部城镇基亚特什莫纳一栋建筑内的平民。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 09:03:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/lebanon-rocket-kills-civilian-in-northern-israel/articleshow/108816514.cms</guid></item><item><title>前内部人士泄露腐败案件录音后，数千人抗议匈牙利欧尔班</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/thousands-protest-against-hungarys-orban-after-former-insider-leaks-graft-case-tape/articleshow/108816714.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108816714.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;抗议者聚集在布达佩斯议会附近，要求首席检察官和总理维克托·欧尔班辞职。在一名前政府内部人士声称欧尔班的一名高级助手试图干预腐败案件后，要求辞职。抗议者高呼“辞职，辞职”，从首席检察官办公室向议会游行，许多人举着火把。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 09:15:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/thousands-protest-against-hungarys-orban-after-former-insider-leaks-graft-case-tape/articleshow/108816714.cms</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩真主党称在以色列袭击后发射了数十枚火箭</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/lebanons-hezbollah-says-it-launched-dozens-of-rockets-after-israeli-strikes/articleshow/108816555.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108816555.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;黎巴嫩真主党证实，本周三早些时候向以色列城镇基里亚特什莫纳发射了多枚火箭，以报复以色列前一天对黎巴嫩南部赫巴里耶村的袭击。自最近以色列与哈马斯在加沙发生冲突以来，以色列和伊朗支持的真主党之间的紧张局势升级，这是自 2006 年以来两派之间最严重的对抗。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 09:07:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/lebanons-hezbollah-says-it-launched-dozens-of-rockets-after-israeli-strikes/articleshow/108816555.cms</guid></item><item><title>泰国议会通过同性婚姻合法化法案</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/bill-to-legalise-same-sex-marriage-passed-by-thailand-parliament/articleshow/108814834.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108814834.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 08:16:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/bill-to-legalise-same-sex-marriage-passed-by-thailand-parliament/articleshow/108814834.cms</guid></item><item><title>“英雄漂浮木板”：泰坦尼克号的门框支柱帮助罗斯保持漂浮，售价为 718,750 美元</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hero-floating-wood-panel-titanics-door-frame-prop-that-helped-rose-stay-afloat-sells-for-718750/articleshow/108812875.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108812875.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;电影《泰坦尼克号》结局中的标志性门框在 Heritage Auctions 拍卖会上以 718,750 美元的惊人价格拍出，超出了预期，创下了拍卖行的拍卖纪录。该道具在佛罗里达州奥兰多的好莱坞星球上展出后，已被存放了近二十年。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 07:30:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hero-floating-wood-panel-titanics-door-frame-prop-that-helped-rose-stay-afloat-sells-for-718750/articleshow/108812875.cms</guid></item><item><title>沙特阿拉伯历史性地首次参加环球小姐选美比赛</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/in-historic-first-saudi-arabia-to-participate-in-miss-universe-pageant/articleshow/108812574.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108812574.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 07:14:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/in-historic-first-saudi-arabia-to-participate-in-miss-universe-pageant/articleshow/108812574.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国政策转变：哈马斯“欢呼”拜登对以色列的新立场</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/shifts-in-us-policy-hamas-hails-bidens-new-stance-on-israel/articleshow/108812424.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108812424.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国打破传统，在以色列与哈马斯冲突期间在联合国“立即停火”投票中投弃权票，导致政策转变。随着国务卿布林肯证明这一决定的合理性，国际社会正在密切关注不断变化的美以动态。哈马斯高级官员将政策转变归因于国际压力和美国国内担忧的结合</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 07:05:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/shifts-in-us-policy-hamas-hails-bidens-new-stance-on-israel/articleshow/108812424.cms</guid></item><item><title>拥有3000年历史的古代仪式金字塔在墨西哥中部揭幕</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/3000-year-old-ancient-ceremonial-pyramid-unveiled-in-central-mexico/articleshow/108813513.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108813513.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;最近在墨西哥中部普埃布拉州进行的考古发掘揭示了 3000 多年前土著社区用于举行仪式的石金字塔。该地点对于监测农业的天文意义得到了证实。尽管遭到破坏，但仍发现了包括烧毁的陶瓷在内的文物。被遗弃后，当地人又回来祭奠祖先。计划进行进一步的研究，该地点仍然不对公众开放。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 07:54:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/3000-year-old-ancient-ceremonial-pyramid-unveiled-in-central-mexico/articleshow/108813513.cms</guid></item><item><title>“塔利班发誓要公开用石头砸死通奸妇女”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/taliban-vows-to-publicly-stone-women-to-death-for-adultery/articleshow/108811767.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108811767.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;塔利班最高领导人毛拉·希巴图拉·阿洪扎达 (Mullah Hibatullah Akhundzada) 重申该组织致力于对妇女采取严厉政策，包括对通奸行为进行公开惩罚。尽管受到国际社会的谴责，塔利班仍以遵守伊斯兰教法为由，继续执行严厉的措施。阿洪扎达的言论标志着对民主价值观和国际准则的蔑视，对人权、特别是阿富汗妇女的人权造成重大挫折。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 06:58:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/taliban-vows-to-publicly-stone-women-to-death-for-adultery/articleshow/108811767.cms</guid></item><item><title>为什么中国的 Z 世代员工在办公室里喜欢穿“恶心的睡衣”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/why-gen-z-workers-in-china-are-embracing-gross-pyjamas-in-offices/articleshow/108809961.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108809961.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 06:10:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/why-gen-z-workers-in-china-are-embracing-gross-pyjamas-in-offices/articleshow/108809961.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦：伊斯兰堡高等法院法官指控三军情报局干涉司法</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-islamabad-hc-judges-allege-isi-interference-in-judiciary/articleshow/108806085.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108806085.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;司法部门和巴基斯坦情报机构三军情报局（ISI）之间出现了公开争端，伊斯兰堡高等法院呼吁对三军情报局涉嫌干涉法律事务的行为采取行动。高等法院已要求最高司法委员会（SJC）召开特别会议来解决所报告的干扰问题。七名伊斯兰堡高等法院法官强调了担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 05:06:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-islamabad-hc-judges-allege-isi-interference-in-judiciary/articleshow/108806085.cms</guid></item><item><title>加密货币盗窃如何帮助朝鲜为其核计划提供资金</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/how-crypto-heists-help-north-korea-fund-its-nuclear-program/articleshow/108807715.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108807715.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国专门小组的报告强调了朝鲜正在进行的网络攻击，六年内净赚 30 亿美元，主要资助其武器计划。拉撒路集团针对大型实体的加密货币盗窃引发了行业担忧。国际网络攻击立法努力面临障碍。韩国加强针对朝鲜网络威胁的安全措施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 04:58:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/how-crypto-heists-help-north-korea-fund-its-nuclear-program/articleshow/108807715.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本2人死亡、100人住院补充恐慌</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/two-deaths-100-hospitalisations-in-japan-supplement-scare/articleshow/108807244.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108807244.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 04:28:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/two-deaths-100-hospitalisations-in-japan-supplement-scare/articleshow/108807244.cms</guid></item><item><title>历史性的防务转变：为什么和平主义的日本现在计划出售战斗机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/historic-defense-shift-why-pacifist-japan-plans-to-sell-fighter-jets-now/articleshow/108807983.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108807983.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;日本政府周二放宽了军事装备出口限制，这是不到四个月内的第二次改变，以允许未来向海外销售其与英国和意大利共同开发的先进喷气式战斗机。这一规则变更仅适用于内阁批准的喷气式战斗机出口，并将仅限于与东京签订国防设备转让协议的国家（目前为 15 个）。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 04:54:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/historic-defense-shift-why-pacifist-japan-plans-to-sell-fighter-jets-now/articleshow/108807983.cms</guid></item><item><title>莫斯科袭击事件后，普京在俄罗斯的形象是否会受到影响？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/after-moscow-attack-could-putins-image-suffer-in-russia/articleshow/108807087.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108807087.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 04:47:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/after-moscow-attack-could-putins-image-suffer-in-russia/articleshow/108807087.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国为俄罗斯的影响力行动做好准备</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-braces-for-russian-influence-operations/articleshow/108806998.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108806998.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;德国在选举前面临越来越多的俄罗斯网络威胁。混合战争结合了军事和非常规战术来影响公众舆论。打击虚假信息和确保网络安全对于应对这些威胁至关重要。</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 04:38:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germany-braces-for-russian-influence-operations/articleshow/108806998.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴西调查雅伊尔·博尔索纳罗在匈牙利大使馆的逗留情况</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/brazil-probes-jair-bolsonaros-stay-at-hungarian-embassy/articleshow/108807542.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108807542.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 04:38:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/brazil-probes-jair-bolsonaros-stay-at-hungarian-embassy/articleshow/108807542.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>